t in several languages including hungarian german japanese and russian and holds a private pilot's license with the federal aviation authority in australia whilst at cddrl andrea will be working for the commission on global election integrity search fsi search within everything courses events fellowships news op eds people publications research other pages recent commentary cddrl's research community expands september 28 2011 cddrl news support map & directions contact rss+ rss xml feeds freeman spogli institute for international studies encina hall 616 serra st stanford ca 94305 6055 tel 650 723 4581 fax 650 725 2592 mail code 6055
